## ansible auto healing web server with syatemd

---
- name: configure autohealing for web server
  hosts: a;;
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: nginx
    state: started
    enabled: yes
    - name: setup auto restart for nginx sevice
      lineinfile:
        path:
	line: "restart=always"
	create:yes
    - name: reload systemd
      command: systmctl daemon-reload


